`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Dual_Wield
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * dual <weapon>

 This is the ability to use a weapon in your off hand.	The weapon must be
lighter than the one wielded in the main hand.	Dual wielding offers the
possibility of added attacks, which means more damage.

